org.llrp.ltk.generated.custom.parameters

Class ImpinjReaderTemperature

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.llrp.ltk.types.LLRPParameter
      • org.llrp.ltk.types.TLVParameter
        • org.llrp.ltk.generated.parameters.Custom
          • org.llrp.ltk.generated.custom.parameters.ImpinjReaderTemperature
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccessCommandOpSpec, AccessCommandOpSpecResult, SpecParameter

    public class ImpinjReaderTemperature
extends Custom
    This custom parameter reports the current temperature of the Reader in degrees Celsius. The temperature that is reported is the internal temperature of the Reader, not the ambient temperature of the Reader surroundings. The temperature is accurate to within +- 2 degrees Celsius across all operating temperatures. See also
